    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>white long grain rice </strong>and <strong>cauliflower rice</strong> to a pot with a lid with 110ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [175ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[225ml]</span> cold water and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Once done, remove from the heat and set aside (lid on) to steam until serving</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sweet-chilli-king-prawn-stir-fry-with-sesame-cauliflower-rice/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely slice (don't chop!) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Deseed your<strong> pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into large bite-sized pieces</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sweet-chilli-king-prawn-stir-fry-with-sesame-cauliflower-rice/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>cornflour</strong> with 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [200ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> in a small bowl</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sweet-chilli-king-prawn-stir-fry-with-sesame-cauliflower-rice/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan or wok (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced garlic</strong>,<strong> chopped pepper</strong> and <strong>sweet pea pods</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until starting to soften</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sweet-chilli-king-prawn-stir-fry-with-sesame-cauliflower-rice/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, drain your <strong>king prawns</strong></p><p>Once the veg is starting to soften, add the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>king prawns</strong> to the pan with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 1-2 min further</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sweet-chilli-king-prawn-stir-fry-with-sesame-cauliflower-rice/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>red chilli relish</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>ketjap manis</strong> and <strong>cornflour mix</strong> to the pan and cook for 3-4 min or until the sauce has thickened and the prawns are cooked through \u2013 this is your <strong>sweet chilli king prawn stir-fry</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sweet-chilli-king-prawn-stir-fry-with-sesame-cauliflower-rice/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is cooked, stir your <strong>black sesame seeds</strong> through \u2013 this is your <strong>sesame rice</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sweet-chilli-king-prawn-stir-fry-with-sesame-cauliflower-rice/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>sweet chilli king prawn stir-fry</strong> with the <strong>sesame cauliflower rice</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
